dataObjects.title: Biology
dataObjects.description: Occurs in small rivers, swamps, and brooks (Ref. 7372).  Not a seasonal killifish.  Is easy to maintain in the aquarium (Ref. 27139).

dataObjects.subject: http://rs.tdwg.org/ontology/voc/SPMInfoItems#Distribution
dataObjects.description: Africa:  Senegal, Gambia, Sierra Leone, Guinea, Liberia, Niger, Nigeria, Côte d'Ivoire, Ghana, Chad, Cameroon and the Central African Republic.  Also known from the White Nile in Sudan (Ref. 7372).  Benin, Togo (Ref. 27139)
